you need to do the following things to run this project.
Follow the steps

1.    create new folder (name whatever you want)
2.    go to the folder and open terminal
3.    run this command "npm init" this will create package.jason files

Install following dependencies by running

-----------------------Solidity Compiler Install Command-------------------

npm install --save solc@0.4.17



------------------------For Local Ethereum Network-------------------------


npm install --save mocha ganache-cli



------------------------For web3 Package-----------------------------------

npm install --save web3@1.0.0-beta.37

#glove glove trade punch potato love tomato tray area employ just pet


------------------------For hdwalled provider------------------------------

npm install --save truffle-hdwallet-provider@0.0.3
